d backup.\n- Fixed downloads not sticking around after restarting.\n\n- Enhanced visuals\n     - Increased resolution.\n     - Improved avatar visuals and support.\n     - Higher quality lighting and reflections.\n     - Refreshed default photo library.\n     - Improved UI visuals.\n     - New sounds too!\n\n- Staying Sharp DLC\n    - Added environment control options.\n          - Available in both paid and free games.\n\nThanks for visiting Alcove!\n\nPlease reach out to alex@rendever.com if you encounter any issues or have feedback.", "created_date": 1713565989, "id": "8608309689183373", "version": "1.300", "version_code": 1300, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": null, "asset_files": {"count": 0}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}, {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "3895528293794893", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "8608309689183373"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": []}, "change_log": null, "created_date": 1713478207, "id": "8603581222989553", "version": "1.260", "version_code": 1260, "release_status": "PENDING", "status": "DRAFT", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": null, "asset_files": {"count": 0}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}, {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "3895528293794893", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "8608309689183373"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": []}, "change_log": null, "created_date": 1713397642, "id": "8599334916747517", "version": "1.250", "version_code": 1250, "release_status": "PENDING", "status": "DRAFT", "b